"19:95:1" : {s: 19, a: 95, w: 1, r: "كلل", t: "وَكُلُّهُمْ", l: "كُلّ", lc: 359, tl: "wakulluhum", lb: "প্রতিটি, সব, প্রত্যেকে ",e: "And all of them", b: "তাদের প্রত্যেকে", f: 1, rm: "To lose father and child, lose direct heirs, be weary, tired, weak, have only remote relations."},
